<h3>Guild Structure<o:p></o:p></h3>

<p>The overall guild structure of Bloodhorde has many facets. We have command
ranks that provide the management of the guild. We have specialized roles to
allow members to focus on detailed tasks. All of these come together to give Bloodhorde
a good framework for destroying our enemies. <o:p></o:p></p>



